precept Test

field counter as integer
field events as log of string

state off initial, running

event create initial
on create
    -> set counter = 0

event start
from off on start
    -> set counter = counter + 1
    -> add events "{now()}:  started"
    -> transition running

event stop  
from running on stop
    -> add events "{now()}:  stopped"
    -> transition off

event reset
from off, running on reset
    -> set counter = 0
    -> clear events
    -> no transition